node.text:
Which car mount is right for you? We've got options for every type of driver! 

Plus, installation is a breeze with ROKFORM mounts. 

Our mounts install in seconds!

Super Grip Vent Mount: Slides over almost any vent. Use any Rokform magnetic case or use the supplied inserts to mount to nearly any phone or case.

Swivel Dash Mount: Installs with easy-to-use residue-free adhesive on any flat surface. Use any Rokform magnetic case or use the supplied inserts to mount to nearly any phone or case.

Windshield Suction Mount and Magnetic Windshield Suction Mount (NEW!): The powerful suction pad allows you to quickly and efficiently install on any flat, non-porous surface. Compatible with all Rokform cases or the Universal Adapter.

Low Pro Magnetic Dash Mount: Installs with easy-to-use residue-free adhesive on any flat surface. Use any Rokform magnetic case, Universal Adapter, or Dual Magnet Universal Adapter.

RokLock Car Dash Mount: Installs with easy-to-use residue-free adhesive on any flat surface. Use any Rokform magnetic case or Universal Adapter.
